    "The true negative (TN) indicates that the marking on images without hand signals has not been detected.",
    "This metric is not considered in our study since, there are no images without hand signs in the dataset.",
    "In order to evaluate the performance of the model trained with all these metric values, the system's precision, recall, F1 score value and mAP values are taken into account.Precision: The ratio of correctly predicted positive results (TP) to all predicted positive results (TP?",
    "Precision value formula:Precision ¼ TP TP þ FPð10ÞRecall: The proportion of correctly predicted positive results.",
    "Recall also measures the precision of the model."
